gr.interamerican.bo2.arch.def
Interface OrderedFieldsContainer

All Known Implementing Classes:
DynamicJdbcQuery, GenericStoredDynamicEntitiesQuery, JdbcCustomAnswerSingleStatementQuestion, JdbcQuery, JdbcStaticQuery, PredefinedReportQuery, StoredDynamicEntitiesQuery, StoredJdbcQuery, XlsRow
public interface OrderedFieldsContainer

Container of fields that have a predefined order. The fields can be accessed using the integer value of their order.
